Project 3

Estructure
    - This project contains 3 main directories where there are placed all the template and Django settings.
    - orders
        . in this directory there are templates and static folder where there are the html code and css files respectively.
    - user 
        . same as orders there are templates and css files
    - pizza
        . python django code
        Those changes include
        *settings.py*: Some additional lines in the end to enable using some additional Features such as *Crispy Forms*.
        *urls.py*: Urlpatterns to include the urls specified in users and orders module.

